
Evidence suggests roulette dealer Billy Jones and roulette player Mylie Schmidt are colluding to defraud the
Lucky Duck casino. Analysis of player data and employee dealer schedules for the week of 10 March
 shows significant losses from the roulette tables for the dates and times below:


