Based on the correlation of the losses at the roulette tables, the records of Mylie Schmidt playing roulette at these times and dates the week of
10 March, and the records showing Billy Jones as working at the roulette tables at these same times strongly suggests that the losses are not
conincidences and that Mylie and Billy are colluding to defraud the Lucky Duck Casino.



